<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">( ... - ١١٢٧ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">( ... - ١٧١٥ م)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
